				\begin{document}$$\left( D \right)_{i} = \sum\nolimits_{j \in N} {a_{ij} } ,$$\end{document}Di=∑j∈Naij,where N is the number of all nodes in the network, aij is the connection value between a pair of nodes (i and j), with aij = 1 when a connection between (i, j) exists, and aij = 0 unless otherwise.
